Slowly coming out of hermit mode, grief and stress over so many variables unknown right now.

So very appreciative of all the kind words, uplifting thoughts, and crappost memes. I'm still here, just a little broken at the moment. 

Keep being awesome for yourself and each other.

Haven't been in touch with a lot of folks in the last six months or so while things have been super heavy and consuming most of my energy and thoughts. 

But it has warmed and revived my soul so much briefly catching up with family members and friends in the last few weeks. <3

Live fiercely.
